  "description": "<ul><li><p><strong>Part Time Stall Service Crew x 3 Headcount</strong></p></li><li><p><em><strong>No Experience Required, On The Job Training Provided</strong></em></p></li><li><p><em><strong>No Pork - Healthy Food Bowls [ Chicken / Beef / Salad / Grain / Wrap ]</strong></em><br /></p><p><br /><u><strong>One Raffles Place - URGENT ‼️‼️</strong></u></p><p><u><strong>7.30am - 2.30pm (Mon - Fri)</strong></u></p><p><u><strong>$ 1700, 30 mins break</strong></u></p><p></p><p><u><strong>Plaza 8 @ Changi Business Park</strong></u></p><p><u><strong>7am - 3pm (Mon - Fri)</strong></u></p><p><u><strong>$ 2000, 30 mins break</strong></u></p><p></p><p><u><strong>One North MRT - Fusionopolis</strong></u></p><p><u><strong>10.30am - 2.30pm (Mon - Thurs)</strong></u></p><p><u><strong>$ 800, no break</strong></u></p><p></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Handle day-to-day operations according to SOP</p></li><li><p>Provide friendly customer service</p></li><li><p><em><strong>Plating food for counter service</strong></em></p></li><li><p>Cooking and mixing rice</p></li><li><p><em><strong>Kitchen preparation work and mise en place</strong></em></p></li><li><p>Stock-taking</p></li><li><p>Replenishing required ingredients</p></li><li><p><em><strong>Cleaning and washing all used service / kitchen tools, equipment and workstations</strong></em></p></li><li><p>Sweeping and mopping<br /></p><p></p></li></ul><p>#SCR-carson-cheong</p><p>⭕ Cheong Kar Chun ⭕ Team Manager ⭕ R1980386</p><p>⭕ The Supreme HR Advisory ⭕ 14C7279</p>",
